<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Tasks — {{FEATURE_TITLE}}</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="spec.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-wrap">

  <nav class="sidebar" aria-label="Table of contents">
    <p class="sidebar-title">Contents</p>
    <div id="toc-list"></div>
  </nav>

  <div class="main-content">
    <header class="spec-header">
      <h1>Implementation tasks — {{FEATURE_TITLE}}</h1>
      <table class="meta-table">
        <tbody>
          <tr><th>Task ID</th>      <td><code>{{TASK_ID}}</code></td></tr>
          <tr><th>Feature slug</th> <td><code>{{FEATURE_SLUG}}</code></td></tr>
          <tr><th>Status</th>       <td><span class="badge badge-draft">spec_draft</span></td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </header>

    <main>

      <section id="tasks">
        <h2>Tasks</h2>
        <p>Implement tasks in the order listed. Each task should be small and independently verifiable.
           Mark tasks complete in <code>tasks.json</code> — this file is the human-readable view.</p>

        <ol class="task-timeline">
          <li class="task-item">
            <div class="task-item-header">
              <span class="req-id t">T1</span>
              <strong>TODO: Add or update tests for requirement <code>REQ-001</code>.</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="task-item-body">Write or update automated tests before implementing to confirm the requirement is currently failing.</div>
          </li>
          <li class="task-item">
            <div class="task-item-header">
              <span class="req-id t">T2</span>
              <strong>TODO: Implement the smallest code change needed for <code>REQ-001</code>.</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="task-item-body">Keep changes focused. Do not expand scope beyond the approved spec.</div>
          </li>
          <li class="task-item">
            <div class="task-item-header">
              <span class="req-id t">T3</span>
              <strong>TODO: Add edge-case handling.</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="task-item-body">Cover the edge cases identified in <code>requirements.html</code>.</div>
          </li>
          <li class="task-item">
            <div class="task-item-header">
              <span class="req-id t">T4</span>
              <strong>TODO: Run validation commands.</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="task-item-body">Run tests, lint, and typecheck as configured in <code>CLAUDE.md</code>.</div>
          </li>
          <li class="task-item">
            <div class="task-item-header">
              <span class="req-id t">T5</span>
              <strong>TODO: Update documentation if needed.</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="task-item-body">Update any user-facing docs or changelog entries that cover this change.</div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section id="validation-checklist">
        <h2>Validation checklist</h2>
        <p>The reviewer verifies each item below before marking the task <code>done</code>.</p>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li><input type="checkbox" disabled> Requirements are covered by tests.</li>
          <li><input type="checkbox" disabled> Tests pass.</li>
          <li><input type="checkbox" disabled> Lint / typecheck pass if configured.</li>
          <li><input type="checkbox" disabled> No protected files were modified without approval.</li>
          <li><input type="checkbox" disabled> Reviewer approved traceability.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

    </main>
  </div><!-- /.main-content -->
</div><!-- /.page-wrap -->
<script src="spec.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
